data.title: Charles Darwin, 1809-1882 : Royal Mail book of stamps / [written by Eugene Byrne ; designed by Howard Brown].
data.meta_description: Booklet containing the stamps issued by the Royal Mail Group Ltd. on Thursday, 12th February 2009 to commemorate the 200th anniversary of the birth of Charles Darwin. All stamps are included, interleaved within a biography of the man and his travels in H.M.S. Beagle.
